high_descs: Walk around to the opposite side of the kitchen island and turn to face it
Pick up the butter knife from the kitchen island
Turn right and walk around to the end of the kitchen island
Put the knife in the wine glass on the kitchen island
Pick up the wine glass from the island
Walk around the island to the kitchen counter by the sink
Put the wine glass on the counter just right of the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the wine glass with knife on the kitchen counter

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the wall, then turn right and walk around to the far side of the kitchen island.
Pick up the metal butter knife that is on the kitchen island in between the sponge and salt shaker.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, then turn left and begin across the room, stop at the end of the kitchen island and turn left to face it.
Put the metal knife in the closest martini glass on the island.
Pick up the glass with the knife in it off of the island.
Turn left and walk around the island to the counter above the dish washer.
Place the glass with the knife in it on the edge of the counter above the dish washer.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with a knife in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left, go straight to the wall, turn right, go straight past the table, turn right, go straight, turn right to face the green table.
Take the small knife between the salt and the sponge from the table.
Turn right, go straight to the wall, turn right, go straight, turn left to face the green table's short side.
Put the knife in the glass on the right side.
Take the glass from the table.
Turn left, go straight to the fridge, turn right, go straight then stop when the sink is to the left.
Put the glass on the counter to the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with a knife in it on a counter.

high_descs: Turn to the left, walk across the room, then turn to the right, walk across the room then turn to the right, walk halfway across the room then turn right to face the table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Turn to the right, walk across the room, turn to the left, take a step, then turn left to face the table.
Put the knife into a glass.
pick up the glass with a knife in it.
Turn to the left, walk across the room, turn to the right, take a small step, then turn to the left, then turn right and take another step, then turn left to face a cabinet.
open the cabinet, put the glass and knife in it, then close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Putting a Knife/glass into a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left then walk towards the wall, turn right then walk towards the refrigerator. Turn right then walk towards the stove, turn right and stand in front of the counter top.
Pick up the knife in front of the salt shaker.
Turn right then walk towards the wall, turn left then walk towards the door, turn left and stand at the green counter top.
Place the knife you are holding, inside the martini glass located by the salt shaker.
Pick up the martini glass with the knife inside located by the salt shaker.
Turn left and walk towards the refrigerator, turn right then walk towards the stove. Stop and stand by the sink.
Place the martini glass with the knife inside on the counter above the dish washer.
anns.task_desc: Place a martini glass with a knife inside on a counter near a dish washer.
